## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online sources, which may not encompass all perspectives on the role of youth in the Beloved Community. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources, potentially excluding valuable insights from non-English speaking regions. Further research, including interviews with youth leaders and community organizers, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.